Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:04.25,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}FLYING IN THE SKY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:09.19,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最高的地方 馳騁於空中的任何角落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:10.92,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.90,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀著光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:16.32,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮大地的盡頭呼喚奇跡的咒語 {\fnComic Sans MS}SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:25.44,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不遲疑的前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:31.72,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有無限的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:39.08,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論嘗試多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:47.51,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多麼痛苦都貫徹到底{\fnComic Sans MS}（G GUNDAM）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.57,0:00:50.63,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛隨時都充斥於這胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:54.21,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.23,0:00:57.32,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙手 咆哮著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:01.31,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向明天飛奔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:03.10,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}BRIGHT YOU NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:08.06,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所描繪的未來之藍圖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:09.80,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:11.60,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:15.34,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部如你所願 {\fnComic Sans MS}I GET A CHANCE！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.82,0:01:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位不介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請容我講解GUNDAM FIGHT的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那起源自6O年前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開被極度污染的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛上宇宙的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了避免衛星國家之間爆發全面戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是創立每四年一度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各國派出代表的Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱名為GUNDAM的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以FIGHT的方式不斷戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後勝出的GUNDAM代表的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能得到衛星國家聯邦的主導權
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然創出充滿體育精神的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，餘下的問題有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這項FIGHT的舞台是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，就是我們居住的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被極度污染的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.54,0:02:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，今屆大賽看來有點不同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的人，你有見過這男人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這照片會掀起多猛烈的戰鬥風暴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日的對手是neo China的Dragon GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但Fighter的身份是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，GUNDAM FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs56}打倒！魔神Dragon GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著，蔡齋西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:03:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在要和Dragon GUNDAM一起降落地球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個宇宙的真正霸主是哪個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要以neo China的名義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出那問題的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要取得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM終於是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來！給我出動吧！黑龍團
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我燒！給我破壞！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把財寶全部搶過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，瑞山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人憤慨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，想不到他會成為盜賊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要走的路畢竟只有一條
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠雲，你看那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的會開槍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙，這班是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道，但是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們有GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵，開動Shining GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄你看來是Gundam Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我冒昧，我有個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了，但不要亂動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，真的很嚴重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠剩下的藥看來不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，多蒙他…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求你！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:06:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你把我們neo China的Gundam Fighter…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得奇怪也難怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我們已經經過反覆考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是留在地球少林寺的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少林寺？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，我們少林寺本來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前是教授世上最強拳法的寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，60年前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分僧人去到衛星上的少林寺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在，那裡只是徒有虛名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我們的住持大師認為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在GUNDAM FIGHT裡漂亮地勝出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要復興少林寺也不是夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是他把年幼的獨子蔡齋西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到衛星上的少林寺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍛練他，賜予他Dragon GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後回到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，事情如你所見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽聞他以山海關做其大本營
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，以免恥辱繼續傳揚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要我殺死他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在GUNDAM FIGHT裡敗北至少是對他的慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我拒絕的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵，我在山海關等你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會答應我們的請求嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔，這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以拿開了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，可以載我一程嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，我要趕時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也趕時間，正好，快點開車啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，老兄，多謝你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真厚臉皮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，另外，你也在旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有見過這男人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是村莊啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄，今日在那裡過夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜，那早晚會給盜賊看中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心，包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別怪我啊，老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日是村莊的節日，很熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好需要人手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則，沒地方讓我們免費留宿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，我正學習廚藝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮菜時順手拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候都不忘撈一把
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟們，今日正好是節日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情給我搶個夠！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那班傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！核戰車被搶去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果，我要和他一較高下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，是為了奪回核戰車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們利用萬里長城的遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為大本營
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，守衛深嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外人不能輕易接近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你非常熟識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我已經調查…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的目的地也在那山寨前面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，我去偵察一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是多謝你載我一程，再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想立功嗎？立功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看，這邊這邊，看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄，老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼？你去了很久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，這傢伙一直鬼鬼崇崇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在查探各位的大本營啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,^_^ 形式所逼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有何目的？講！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，潑水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？你想講了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標不是你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的目標是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是駕駛Dragon GUNDAM的蔡齋西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到不利用這些手下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能和我分勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣，惠雲和瑞山會很傷心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我在GUNDAM FIGHT裡分勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，你也有GUNDAM吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我現在馬上解決你！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，把他關進監牢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子，你也和那傢伙一夥的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕…絕對不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是個流浪廚師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽聞首領你武功高強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心想能為你們煮菜燒飯就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，隨便你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的關係到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子的廚藝的確不俗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…兄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在我拿飯給你份上，你原諒我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣做全是為了潛入這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待我替你開鎖證明給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧，跟著隨你怎喜歡怎做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核戰車在正門旁的倉庫裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了！有人逃獄呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑…卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙逃獄了！他逃出來了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他奪回核戰車！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想多謝你幫我保管我的貴重物品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM FIGHT國際條約第四條
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Fighter有責任保護自己的GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只要找出蔡齋西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon GUNDAM！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，全靠老兄你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才能奪回我的GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，你就是…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是如假包換的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔡齋西！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實，當我們從衛星飛下來時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一點小意外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我醒來時便發覺我和GUNDAM降落在不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然平安著陸是好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它卻被盜賊利用為工具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你便利用我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我在FIGHT裡好好報答你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，GUNDAM FIGHT準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動掃瞄系統開動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦波、血壓、心跳、呼吸、體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新陳代謝機能全部正常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，看我的Dragon GUNDAM初次出戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點本事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣，我也明白少林寺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何把復興的夢想托負給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使對手是老兄你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會留情啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起，老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是旗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪裡！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄，你能看見我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些旗在擾亂我的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你輸了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必殺！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這隻手在閃耀和咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在高聲叫我打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，認輸吧，蔡齋西！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場比賽是打和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則，你也會失去你的頭部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:20:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若老兄你不介意，我也可撒手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙總愛口舌之爭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，今日就打和吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次真的非常多謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盜賊們已經交給本地的警衛隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩人會引導及鍛練蔡齋西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令他有資格成為少林寺的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及避免再發生同類事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你原諒他對你的無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看來也毫無關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只是neo France和neo Russia
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.15,0:21:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我一定會找出這個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，莉茵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:32.20,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便數千的日夜流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:36.59,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所到達的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.84,0:22:41.03,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨著 追求著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:44.60,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫步著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:51.75,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人啊 在我瞳孔的深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:57.45,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實搖曳著的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.65,0:23:02.76,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如何傳達才好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.78,0:23:09.24,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓受傷的心與身體
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.65,0:23:13.42,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這溫暖的懷抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.55,0:23:19.41,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比海更深沉的睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了向華麗的Gundam Fighter喬爾殊·山度挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙綁架了他侍奉的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憤怒的他以GUNDAM Rose英姿颯爽地出場
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以巴黎為舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎士道和武士道激烈碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.20,0:23:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 機動武鬥傳G GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.10,0:23:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決一勝負！鮮紅玫瑰的貴公子！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.50,0:23:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！


